channel.title: Port 43594 already in use -- portforwarding problem!
channel.description:
Hi, I portforwarded but when I try to login to server it says port 43594 already in use.
- I tryed more than 1 server. - There was no other servers running when I tryed. - I restarted my computer and tryed.
I really want to host a server but I need to get past this problem, please someone help me..
